item.title: Need help! please check!
item.dc:creator: @Tom Tom
item.description:
@Tom wrote:

The server may be rejecting the client, check what is printed on the CMD. Some servers only allow certain clients to connect based on UID. Or the client could have something missing the server needs to allow a login.

But check what the server is saying when the client connects and post it here.

Read full topic
